About the job
Responsibilities:

Develop and maintain high-quality front-end code for websites and applications.
Create, customize, and maintain WordPress themes to meet project requirements.
Optimize websites for performance, speed, and responsiveness across devices.
Troubleshoot and debug issues in JavaScript, WordPress themes, and front-end code.

About the job
Key Responsibilities:

Proficiency in HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript to create dynamic and interactive web experiences.

Incorporate interactivity, animations, and transitions to enhance user engagement and usability.

Ensure brand consistency across all digital touchpoints by following brand guidelines and design standards.

Ensure cross-browser compatibility

Ensure designs are visually appealing, user-friendly, and responsive across various devices and screen sizes

Troubleshoot and debug frontend issues for optimal performance.

Required Skills:

Strong proficiency in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

Experience with jQuery and Bootstrap frameworks.

Familiarity with responsive design principles.

Ability to collaborate in a team-oriented environment.
